pages.title: Tipue Search, a site search engine jQuery plugin
pages.text: Tipue Search is a site search engine jQuery plugin. It's free, open source, responsive and fast. Tipue Search only needs a browser that supports jQuery. It doesn't need MySQL or similar. In Static mode it doesn't even need a web server.

pages.title: Tipue Search Documentation
pages.text: Tipue Search is a site search engine jQuery plugin. It's free, open source, responsive and fast. Tipue Search uses various modes for loading content. Static mode uses a JavaScript object, while JSON mode uses JSON. Live mode grabs content from a list of pages dynamically.
